WHAT IS DATA TYPE?
data type define the type of value  a varible can store in program
______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
TYPES OF DATA TYPES
1)primitive  data type
2) non primitive  data type 

1) PRIMITIVE DATA TYPE
A primitive data type is a basic, built-in data type that stores a simple value directly in memory.It is not made up of other data types.
primitive data types are NUMERIC,BOOLEAN

